name: Let's Go Rocket
description:
Let's Go Rocket, the must play one-touch rocket game, over a 200 million games played so far!

Touch to launch and boost your rocket, avoid the obstacles and see how far you can fly!

- What's your high-score?
- Collect the gems
- Beat your friends
- Unlock and play with 38 amazing rockets
- So let's go...Let's Go Rocket

More
Discover more amazing Cobra Mobile games at www.cobramobile.com

Support
Having problems? Visit http://www.cobramobile.com/support/ to see if we can help you.


PLEASE NOTE: Let's Go Rocket is free to download and play (aside from internet, carrier, data, device, and other services for which the player is financially responsible), but some in-game items can be purchased with real money. You can turn off the payment feature by disabling in-app purchases in your device's settings, or reach us at "support@cobramobile.com" for help.
